{"tid":193066,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"飛圖一代K后　投資損手逾千萬 48歲梁雁翎復出開騷","createTime":"2017-04-09T04:58:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-10T09:55:19.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fc177a5d38f59bdf15cf0d4a643c7d4c380575d3","tid":193066,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:58:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20170409/large/09ec1p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20170409%2Flarge%2F09ec1p1.jpg&h=8db20bff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n那些年卡拉OK在香港掀起熱潮，始祖飛圖唱片股東兼歌手梁雁翎被封K后，其金曲《像霧像雨又像風》、《你歌我歌》晚晚向觀眾洗腦，在無綫廣告時段滾筒式狂播，自飛圖賣盤、嫁醫生老公後退出樂壇，梁雁翎經歷過投資失敗逾千萬。神隱多年的她捲土重來，48歲再踏舞台於下月假麥花臣場館開騷。<br />\n<br />\n現年48歲的梁雁翎生於北京，85年參選第一屆亞洲小姐入行，之後轉戰樂壇投資成立飛圖唱片，成功打開卡拉OK市場做K后。神隱多年的她日前在觀塘的K房接受《蘋果》專訪，當年一把長髮，現在只過膊頭，但兩鬢蠟起的招牌髮型不變，做出招牌台風連唱K歌《像霧像雨又像風》和《你歌我歌》，風采依然。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170409/19984207?_ga=1.214019159.1569118513.1441089978\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170409%2F19984207%3F_ga%3D1.214019159.1569118513.1441089978&d=Ih%2BYJd3WmO0qFhbj2imzB4M9LuuOiGKVuJxWWRW4JEQ%3D&h=8446e6fc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20170409%2F19984207%3F_ga%3D1.214019159.1569118513.1441089978&h=b5852413\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20170409/19984207?_ga=1.214019159.1569118513.1441089978</a>"},{"pid":"f90168bddf76641453bfdbd3058bca233e6f6a64","tid":193066,"uid":78429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:06:17.000Z","msg":"好快梅艷芳，張國榮，黃霑果啲全部出返哂嚟"},{"pid":"3dc86103071f1b15d915909fb4b3d2aa5041b40d","tid":193066,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T08:28:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif